      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MISS ARIZONA (7) finished well back at Maitland last time when a 8 length sixth (22.86) but scored three back at Maitland (22.22). Has a good winning strike rate at this journey. Should bounce back. RAPID LULU (4) has been in super consistent form, last time breaking from this same box when second in a Grade 5 at this track (20.04) and making it three straight placings. Harder here but will be in this for a long way. REEL 'EM ZENA (1) finds it hard to break through. Finished in the minors latest when third (20.57) at this track and may be close to breaking through. Expected to be in the finish again. MID CITY BOSS (2) flew the lids and led all the way last time. Sure to figure prominently.",
